    <th>Result.Id</th><th>Result.NS.Id</th><th>Result.EW.Id</th><th>Result.TableNumber</th><th>Result.RoundNumber</th><th>Result.NumberOfTricks</th><th>Result.ContractColor</th><th>esult.ContractLevel</th>
